      <title>特斯拉因汽车排放标准主张退出澳大利亚汽车游说团体</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-quits-australia-auto-lobby-over-claims-car-emission-standards-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉周四表示，将退出澳大利亚主要汽车游说团体并辞去董事会职务，指责该团体在政府提议的燃油效率标准及其对汽车价格的潜在影响方面误导消费者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-quits-australia-auto-lobby-over-claims-car-emission-standards-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 04:22:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚政府敦促赋予监管机构分拆超市巨头的权力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australia-government-urged-give-regulator-power-break-up-supermarket-giants-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院周四听取了一项调查，澳大利亚反垄断监管机构应有权分拆超市巨头 Woolworths 和 Coles，以改善竞争，因为水果和蔬菜种植者已经 15 年没有看到价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australia-government-urged-give-regulator-power-break-up-supermarket-giants-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:59:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港法官驳回亲民主电台主持人煽动叛乱案上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-judges-dismiss-appeal-sedition-case-pro-democracy-radio-host-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，三名香港高等法院法官驳回了著名民主活动人士谭德志的上诉，谭德志因 11 项煽动叛乱罪被定罪并被判 40 个月，他的律师辩称这些罪名是对言论自由的不成比例的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-judges-dismiss-appeal-sedition-case-pro-democracy-radio-host-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将为休带薪育儿假的工人缴纳养老金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-make-pension-contributions-workers-paid-parental-leave-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚周四表示，将为休带薪育儿假的工人缴纳养老金，这是中左翼工党政府解决工作场所性别失衡问题的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-make-pension-contributions-workers-paid-parental-leave-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:31:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本主要工会赢得部分成员大幅加薪，谈判仍在继续</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-major-union-wins-big-pay-hikes-some-members-talks-continue-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本最大的工业劳工组织周四表示，迄今为止，其 25 个成员工会已完全满足管理层的工资要求，并同意在下周结束的年度工资谈判中将全职工人的工资提高 6.7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-major-union-wins-big-pay-hikes-some-members-talks-continue-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国企业集团复星旗下旅游部门表示正在审查业务组合</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-conglomerate-fosuns-tourism-unit-says-reviewing-business-portfolio-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[复星旅文集团周四表示，正在审查其业务组合，以回应路透社有关其正在探索出售酒店度假村的报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-conglomerate-fosuns-tourism-unit-says-reviewing-business-portfolio-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:09:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将向六国旅客提供免签待遇</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-offer-visa-free-travel-travellers-six-countries-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外交部长王毅周四表示，中国将从3月14日起向瑞士、爱尔兰、匈牙利、澳大利亚、比利时和卢森堡公民提供免签旅行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-offer-visa-free-travel-travellers-six-countries-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:05:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市因美国降息而上涨，日元因日本央行的言论而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最有权势的央行行长向投资者保证美国利率今年将下降，为欧洲政策制定者奠定了基础，亚洲股市周四上涨，而美元则下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:35:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>防务报告称，中国加强灰色地带战以消耗台湾资源</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-steps-up-grey-zone-warfare-exhaust-taiwan-defence-report-says-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾国防部周四的一份报告称，中国加强了针对台湾的灰色地带战，旨在让这个民主岛屿周围的地区充满气球、无人机和民用船只。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-steps-up-grey-zone-warfare-exhaust-taiwan-defence-report-says-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:40:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元因日本央行即将转向支点的可能性而上涨；美元普遍走低</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-falls-with-treasury-yields-views-looming-us-rate-cuts-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元兑美元汇率周四升至一个月高位，原因是越来越多的人猜测日本央行(BOJ)可能最早在本月结束负利率，以及美国即将降息的押注拖累美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-falls-with-treasury-yields-views-looming-us-rate-cuts-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:21:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
